"{\"uid\": \"app.com.pk-national-saudi-envoy-congratulates-pakistan-on-arshad-nadeems-historic-olympic-gold\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Rehan Khan  ISLAMABAD, Aug 10 (APP): Saudi Press Attach\\u00e9, Dr. Naif Al-Otaibi has extended his warmest congratulations to the people of Pakistan on Arshad Nadeem's historic achievement of winning Gold Medal at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 231, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3, \"end\": 13, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rehan_Khan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rehan Khan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rehan_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rehan_Khan\"}, {\"begin\": 34, \"end\": 37, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Application_software\", \"score\": 0.99959777860452, \"rank\": 0.00040233780677101816, \"text\": \"APP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Application_software\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Application_software\"}, {\"begin\": 40, \"end\": 45, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.99999086593413, \"rank\": 9.08997653672031e-06, \"text\": \"Saudi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 59, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Publicity\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Press Attach\\u00e9\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Publicity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Publicity\"}, {\"begin\": 65, \"end\": 69, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naif\", \"score\": 0.9999996758907016, \"rank\": 3.2410934581219513e-07, \"text\": \"Naif\", \"types\": [\"Q532\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Naif\"}, {\"begin\": 138, \"end\": 146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999975795928737, \"rank\": 2.340616869566658e-06, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In his congratulatory message on Saturday, he said Arshad Nadeem, the Pakistani javelin thrower, achieved a monumental feat by breaking the Olympic record with a throw of 92.97 meters, bringing immense pride to his nation.\", \"from\": 233, \"to\": 455, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 297, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arshad Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Al-Otaibi praised Arshad Nadeem for his outstanding performance, describing it as a significant milestone not only for Pakistan but for the entire Muslim world.\", \"from\": 457, \"to\": 621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 580, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999975795928737, \"rank\": 2.340616869566658e-06, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}, {\"begin\": 608, \"end\": 614, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"score\": 0.7612558056071068, \"rank\": 0.30829356958326165, \"text\": \"Muslim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Muslims\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This historic win is a testament to the resilience and dedication of the people of Pakistan,\\\" he remarked.\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 729, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 706, \"end\": 714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999975795928737, \"rank\": 2.340616869566658e-06, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dr. Al-Otaibi also highlighted the close brotherly relations between Saudi Arabia and Pakistan, adding that the success of Pakistani athletes was celebrated with great joy in the Kingdom.\", \"from\": 731, \"to\": 918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 806, \"end\": 812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.9999800774296144, \"rank\": 1.992267280162324e-05, \"text\": \"Arabia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 817, \"end\": 825, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999975795928737, \"rank\": 2.340616869566658e-06, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}, {\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_at_the_2010_Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999890214301212, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Pakistani athletes\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_at_the_2010_Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan_at_the_2010_Asian_Games\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He expressed his hope that this victory would inspire further achievements and strengthen the bonds of friendship between the two nations.\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 1057, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Saudi press Attach\\u00e9 wished continued success to Pakistan in the field of sports, emphasizing the shared pride in Arshad Nadeem's remarkable accomplishment on the global stage.\", \"from\": 1059, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1063, \"end\": 1068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"score\": 0.99999086593413, \"rank\": 9.08997653672031e-06, \"text\": \"Saudi\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saudi_Arabia\"}, {\"begin\": 1111, \"end\": 1119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"score\": 0.9999975795928737, \"rank\": 2.340616869566658e-06, \"text\": \"Pakistan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pakistan\"}, {\"begin\": 1176, \"end\": 1189, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Arshad Nadeem\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arshad_Nadeem\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serving the nation since 1947 by providing an accurate, objective, uninterrupted flow of news to the people, the national news service is pursuing a comprehensive strategy to transform the existing news operations into a forward-looking service - APP Digital for its diverse subscriber-base and the public.\", \"from\": 1240, \"to\": 1546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Contact us:news@app.com.pk  Copyright \\u00a9 Associated Press of Pakistan\", \"from\": 1548, \"to\": 1616, \"entities\": []}]}"